data: Arrr, ye landlubbers! So ye be wantin' to know about attendance, eh? Well, let me tell ye, attendance be mandatory on this here ship... I mean, course. Ye gotta show up fer every class, or ye might as well walk the plank! The instructor will be checkin' attendance every class, so make sure ye don't miss any unless ye have a good reason fer doin' so, and even then, ye should let 'em know in advance. So hoist the sails and get yer booty to class, or ye might find yerself swabbin' the decks instead!

data:
Ahoy matey! Ye be wonderin' how yer grade be gettin' calculated, eh? Well, listen close and I'll tell ye. The grading o' this course be based on three main components, like a treasure chest overflowin' with booty!

First, we have assignments, which account fer 40% o' yer final grade. Make sure ye complete them all, or walk the plank!

Next, we got midterm exams, weighin' in at 30%. So, hoist the sails and get ready to test yer knowledge, matey!

Last but not least, we have the final exam, makin' up the other 30% o' yer grade. It be a big one, so don't ye be slippin' up!

So there ye have it, me hearty! That be how the grading be handled in this here course. Fair winds and following seas to all ye students!
